I"ð<ol>
  <li>Edit <code class="highlighter-rouge">/etc/default/grub</code>:
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX="net.ifnames=0 biosdevname=0"
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Run: <code class="highlighter-rouge">update-grub</code>.</li>
  <li>Edit <code class="highlighter-rouge">/etc/network/interfaces</code> and rename interface to <code class="highlighter-rouge">eth0</code>.</li>
  <li>Reboot</li>
</ol>

